<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.1">
<l>cītak kaṭaluḷ ḷamutaṉṉa tēvaki</l>
<l>kōtaik kuḻalā ḷacōtaikkup pōttanta</l>
<l>pētaik kuḻavi piṭittuc cuvaittuṇṇum</l>
<l>pātak kamalaṅkaḷ kāṇīrē pavaḷavā yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with coral-red mouths, see the lotus-feet that are seized</l>
<l>and sucked and tasted [by] the innocent babe</l>
<l>who was sent to Yaśodā, with a garland in her curly hair, [by] Devakī</l>
<l>who is like the nectar in the cool sea. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
